snippet.title: EXPLOSIVE claims in new book about Prince Charles, Prince Harry and Meghan Markle | Sunrise
snippet.description:
A new book has made major claims about the royal family -- stating which member triggered the rift with Meghan Markle and Prince Harry. the book, by Christopher Andersen, claims to have details about private conversations between Prince Charles and Camilla.
